{"timestamp": "2025-12-04 15:45:47.174070", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission summary:\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): host_1_1_1_1\n- Root cause: host_missing_ip\n\nRationale:\n- host_1_1_1_1 shows no IPv4 address and no default route despite the design requiring a static address in 10.1.1.0/24. This isolates the host from L3 communication.\n- OSPF fabric, server farm services (DNS/HTTP), and other hosts’ connectivity appear healthy, indicating the issue is localized to the endpoint configuration rather than network infrastructure.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1915, "output_tokens": 123, "total_tokens": 2038, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1792}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
